{"tid":2270008,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"深入淺出–跳躍掠針蟻","createTime":"2020-11-03T22:43:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-06T12:35:04.000Z","uid":38861,"like":44,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"cee6b5525cdd8884fcf918c7f94331c9caa80082","tid":2270008,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T22:43:18.000Z","msg":"為慶祝螞蟻金服延期在港交所上市，今集我們會講解一種頗為特別的螞蟻品種&ndash;跳躍掠針蟻(Harpegnathos saltator)。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6sHL1oj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6sHL1oj.jpg&h=ae69fab6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（圖2）螞蟻是社交性動物，各司其職。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1cn0QgH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1cn0QgH.jpg&h=adfb8bc3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n蟻后一大群工蟻是的統領，管治一道族群，主職生蛋生育，而工蟻則負責出外捕獵食物，把糧食送到帶到巢穴。<br />\n<br />\n當蟻后死去後，跳躍掠針蟻的其中一隻工蟻便會擔當蟻后的角色，維持族群安寧，而這個偽蟻后我們稱之為Gamergate。<br />\n<br />\n這種工蟻轉變成偽蟻后的現象，暫時只有在跳躍掠針蟻這品種能夠觀察得到，並沒能在其他螞蟻品種中觀察得到。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（圖3）這種獨特的現象自當然引起各科學家的興趣。而有科學家發現（Ref1)，Worker轉變成為Gamergate後，腦部的Corazonin蛋白質含量會大幅度下降;<br />\n往Worker腦部注射Corazonin蛋白質的話，則會減低螞蟻的潛在生蛋能力。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rWiOY98.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrWiOY98.jpg&h=4bb6da6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而最為匪夷所思的是，當Worker轉變成為Gamergate後，其平均壽命會由5個月遞升至3年有多!<br />\n<br />\n由工蟻變成偽蟻后的確切機制，現今一直還在發掘之中，其腦部結構性的轉變相信是扮演著非常重大的角色。<br />\n<br />\n如果想我快啲出文的話，請入去Penana網站<span class=\"blue\">科普專欄&ndash;薯不揀單</span>俾一個<span class=\"green\">like</span>以及<span class=\"red\">Bookmark</span>，這對我非常之重要。<br />\n<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fstory%2F66244%2F%25E7%25A7%2591%25E6%2599%25AE%25E5%25B0%2588%25E6%25AC%2584-%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%258F%2580%25E5%2596%25AE%2Ftoc&d=O3JFyT0uW1vU8ssvO3VcyhmaKe8vvTAxx9uYoYxOzRs%3D&h=9d9ae5c9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc</a><br />\n<br />\n同時亦可以在Penana網站裡按「<span class=\"gold\">買一嚿/半嚿薯仔</span>」，以課金的方式推動我繼續搜羅資料寫文，多謝。<br />\n<br />\nLink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fuser%2F27349%2F%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25BB%2594%25E8%2581%259E%25E8%258C%25B1%25E8%258E%2589%2Fportfolio&d=O3JFyT0uW1vU8ssvO3VcyhmaKe8vvTAxx9uYoYxOzRs%3D&h=d99ea4b0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有興趣接收科學資訊的話，歡迎follow IG: potatopigtongue。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/potatopigtongue/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fpotatopigtongue%2F&d=O3JFyT0uW1vU8ssvO3VcyhmaKe8vvTAxx9uYoYxOzRs%3D&h=3bd5ea9e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/potatopigtongue/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nRef1:<a href=\"https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/28802044/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2F28802044%2F&d=O3JFyT0uW1vU8ssvO3VcyhmaKe8vvTAxx9uYoYxOzRs%3D&h=a8e4f99f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/28802044/</a>"},{"pid":"86b3907f14762e86c4581aa8b5de6ce5232dc2f4","tid":2270008,"uid":35620,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T23:06:16.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"2ae2053f8982d549f65421b083038538d28ec46a","tid":2270008,"uid":35620,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T23:06:55.000Z","msg":"以前養過蟻，見到淘寶有呢種買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50305d0944418e93a576821b826f605f89cce05c","tid":2270008,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote